		<p>I&#8217;m still more excited about CLIC because of its potential to introduce new technology that might pave the way for more powerful future colliders, but ILC is interesting too.  I wonder if exploring the Higgs and its decays is enough work to justify such a large project in the eyes of the public.  Maybe there will be more things to investigate if the upgraded LHC turns up some interesting anomalies.</p>

